items.headline: Welcome to the Factpile Wiki!
items.desc: Factpile wiki is your number one resource for all things having to do with Factpile. You can track the fantasy match ups of your favorite Video Game, Comic, TV, Book or Movie characters and see how they fare on the main Factpile site. You can also check out character profiles, as well as information on your fellow pilers, stuff, major events that often happen on both the mainland on the 'topia, and FactPile Culture and various terms of it blah blah blah.
